dc_title_s: Riparian map of mid-Atlantic coast, bays, and estuaries, featuring Toms River and adjacent areas
dc_description_s: This is a map of the coastal area around Toms River and Long Beach Island showing water depth information for Toms River, Barnegat Bay, and part of the Atlantic Ocean. It also marks suitable areas for hunting and fishing and notes several life saving stations along Long Beach Island.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
